summary: An Ordinance appropriating Two Thousand Four Hundred Sixty-two Dollars and Sixty-two cents ($2462.62) to pay into the registry of the court certain awards, interest and costs in Cause No. 87583 under Ordinance No. 29364, and directing the City Comptroller to draw and the City Treasurer to pay a warrant on the general fund therefor in favor of W. K. Sickels, County Clerk, and declaring an emergency.
